[[File:LEGOFlashbulbCamera.jpg|thumb|right|A [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] snapping a picture with an instant camera.]]
An '''instant camera''' was a type of [[Camera/Legends|recording device]] which captured a still image of an event and then printed it on a small page of [[Paper/Legends|paper]]. This piece of paper would then be ejected from the camera. A flash of light was also released simultaneously with the recording, presumably to provide additional brightness to the captured image.

A device of this type was used by an unknown [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] in an unknown [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]], to take a picture of [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Jedi Master/Legends|Master]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and fellow [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]]. However, the printed image was not that of the two friends; instead, the printout showed a picture of an aged Obi-Wan dueling Darth Vader.

